snippet.title: Persona 5 Strikers - Opening Cinematic Animation (2021)
snippet.description:
This is the opening cinematic animation for Persona 5 Strikers. The first thing we will see when the game launches next month! Can't Wait!

►NOTE - This is footage that CGInferno sent me, and am featuring it on the channel with his permission. I do not have the game early. Check out CG's channel - https://www.youtube.com/c/cginferno
